title: FOLFOX responder training, #211
source_name_ch1: tumor sample of patients with unresectable CRC before mFOLFOX6 therapy
treatment_protocol_ch1: Surgical specimens were immediately cut into small pieces after resection, snap frozen in liquid nitrogen, and stored at –80°C
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Experimental procedures for GeneChip(TM) were performed in accordance with the GeneChip Expression Analysis Technical Manual (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA), using 3 µg of total RNA.
hyb_protocol: Hybridization was performed according to standard protocols for Affymetrix HG-U133 plus 2.0 arrays. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner 7G.
data_processing: The data were analyzed with Affymetrix Power Tools (APT version:1.12.0). The apt-probeset-summarize command were used with -a plier-mm-sketch option.
contact_department: Research Center for Advanced Science and Technology
